The paper deals with joint understanding of video and language, which is a common theme in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed Mixture-of-Embedding-Experts (MEE) model is a deep learning architecture, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on the task of video retrieval, which is a common task in information retrieval (cs.IR).
